<td data-valign="top"><p><span id="img_07400"></span> <img src="img/07400.jpg" alt="C" /></p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>CUIREAM fionn-faoilidh umam,<br />
A thraoghadh feirge falamh,<br />
A chumail rium mo chliu,<br />
Fad ’s a bhios mi biu air talamh.</p>
<p>O Mhicheil! glac mo lamh,<br />
Liobh rium cairdeas De,<br />
Ma tha mi-run no di-run air mo namh,<br />
Criosd a bhi eadar mis is e,<br />
     O, Criosd eadar mis is e!</p>
<p>Ma tha mi-run no di-run air mo sgath,<br />
Criosd a bhi eadar mis is e,<br />
     O, Criosd eadar mis is e!</p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p> </p></td>
<td data-valign="top"><p>I PLACE the 'fionn-faoilidh' on me,<br />
To drain wrath empty,<br />
To preserve to me my fame,<br />
While I shall live on earth.</p>
<p>O Michael! grasp my hand,<br />
Vouchsafe to me the love of God,<br />
If there be ill-will or ill-wish in mine enemy,<br />
Christ be between me and him,<br />
     Oh, Christ between me and him!</p>
<p>If there be ill-will or ill-wish concerning me,<br />
Christ be between me and it,<br />
     Oh, Christ between me and it!</p></td>
